http://www.savers.org:80/nationalreview/09oct95/feature.html 204.71.237.73 19970108070056 text/html 30478
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 07:01:09 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 02-Aug-96 17:52:49 GMT
