<br>
 phone: 202-785-0238  fax: 202-822-8118
<br>
World Wide Web: http://www.sbsc.org     email: rstikes@sbsc.org
</h5>
</center></td><td width="35%">
<font size="-1">
National Education Association leadership has so far during this campaign cycle contributed 99% of its PAC money to Democrats. 
<br><center>John E. Berthaud 
<br>Vice President Alexis de 
<br>Tosqueville Institution
</font>
</td></tr></table></center>
<BR>
<center>| <a href="/sbsc/laborwatch/welcome.html">Labor Watch Index</a> | <a href="/sbsc/">Home</a> |</center>
</center>
</blockquote>
