<title>August 7, 1996 Press Release</title>

<body>

<font size=-1>

FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE<br>
August 7, 1996<br>
CONTACT: Kristi S. Hamrick -- (202) 393-2100. In San Diego: Kristin 
