<p>

<center><h2>WHO STANDS FOR CHILDREN<br>
AND WHERE DO THEY STAND</h2>

<p>

<h4>Pro-Family Groups to Answer These Questions and more regarding
the Children's Defense Fund &quot;Stand for Children&quot; Rally
scheduled for June 1.

<p>

