<p>

For a pro-family perspective on this march on Washington and
the issues children most struggle with join family advocates:

<p>

When: May 31, 1996 at 9:30 a.m.<br>
Where: National Press Club, First Amendment Room<br>
Who: National Leaders and Ordinary Families,<br>
to be announced.

<p>

