<title>Family Research Council FAQ</title>

<body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000">

<center><h2>Family Research Council FAQ (Frequently Asked 
Questions)</h2></center>

<ol><h4>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq1.html">Why does FRC exist and 
what do they stand for?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq2.html">What does FRC think about 
AIDS funding?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq3.html">What does FRC think about 
adoption?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq4.html">What does FRC think about 
child care?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq5.html">What does FRC think about 
China having "most favored nation" trade status?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq6.html">What does FRC think about 
crime prevention?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq7.html">What does FRC think about 
defunding public arts and humanities that support cultural decay?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq8.html">What is FRC's stand on 
divorce reform?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq9.html">What national drug abuse 
policies does FRC support?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq10.html">How does FRC believe we 
can improve the public education system in America?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq11.html">What solutions does FRC 
see for affordable health care?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq12.html">What is FRC's response to 
the homosexual agenda?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq13.html">What is FRC's position on 
the military's homosexual ban?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq14.html">What does FRC think can 
be done to restore the sanctity of human life?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq15.html">How does FRC view 
immigration reform?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq16.html">What is FRC's position 
on the Legal Services Corporation?</a>

