X of the Public Health Service Act?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq25.html">What is FRC's position 
on the United Nations' Convention on the Rights of the Child?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq26.html">Does FRC support the 
adoption of a $500 per child tax credit for every American family 
with children?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq27.html">Does FRC support welfare 
reform? Why?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq28.html">Does FRC support exemptions 
for women in combat?</a>

<li><a href="/townhall/FRC/faq/faq29.html">What is FRC's position on 
informed consent for women's reproductive health decisions?</a>

</h4></ol>

If you have any questions or comments about the Family Research 
Council that are not answered here, please feel free to 
<a href="/townhall/FRC/email/email.html">email</a> us -- we'll be 
glad to answer them for you.

