<H2>Convicts' Counsel</H2>
</CENTER>
<P>
<blockquote>




"Charleston (WV)The state Supreme Court said the state can't enforce a smoking ban at regional jails because the rule was adopted without inmates' input."
<P>
<I>USA Today</I>, December 10, 1996



</blockquote>
