<P><center>
<H2>Shameless</H2>
</CENTER>
<P>
<blockquote>







	


	"Last week, President Clinton announced he was designating October 1219 'National Character Counts Week.' Clinton remarked on the day of the pronouncement, 'During this special week, we recognize that character is not a quality we are born with; we must learn it.' "


<P>
<I>Human Events</I>, October 25, 1996


</blockquote>
