<title>July-August 1996 Insider -- Resource Bank -- Heritage</title>
</HEAD>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/heritage/paperh.jpg">
<P>
<center>
<img src="/heritage/thf_log2.gif"><P>
<h3>Resource Bank</h3><br>
from the July-August 1996  Edition of <i>The Insider</i><p>
<a name="table"></a>
<h2>Publication Reviews</h2><p></center>
